  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<b>Takasu Haruko, Mitsuko and Katsuko</b> are the daughters of Taiga and
    Ryuuji. They''re the grand oddity of the family, having been born as identical
    triplets. Their bodies are peculiar, growing taller than their father, curvier
    than their mother and towering over all the boys and girls they meet. No matter
    where they are, whether it be with family or in school, they will always stick
    out!


    The sisters have always had a hard time fitting in with their peers,
    from the start of elementary school to the end of junior high. They''d end up
    as punching bags for those around them, with their strange appearances, offputting
    personalities and academic ineptitude. In the end, the sisters only had one another
    to keep themselves company, like three peas in a pod. It was the only way of
    survival they knew.


    When they enrolled into Ohashi High School, it seemed
    things were going to be no different... but that couldn''t be further from the
    truth. Fate was pulling each of the sisters in different directions. When faced
    with this predicament, they had to decide whether keep this sisterly trifecta
    together, or let it crumble so they can forge their own paths.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 82abf587aec7f1b439a4ac0c432f2e7a, type: 2}
