  m_text: '"Toranoko!" by InfernalFury270 (IF270) is a fan fiction of "Toradora!"
    by Takemiya Yuyuko.

    

    It''s a spinoff-sequel that with a new, wide
    cast of characters, taking place 20 years after the events of the original series.


    On
    this website, you can learn about the series, read "Toranoko!" content or check
    out the characters!


    This is the WebGL version of the website.

    

'
